Used to change the permissions on a file or directory
make a file executable for all and writeable by the owner
chmod 755 file
make a file read write for owner
chmod 600 file
make a file read write for owner and readable for everyone else
chmod 644 file
make a file readonly for the owner
chmod 400 file

The file permissions are owner group everyone
755 is rwxr-xr-x
600 is rw-------
644 is rw-r--r--
